# solarized color scheme for newsbeuter <http://www.newsbeuter.org/>
# more on solarized: http://ethanschoonover.com/solarized

color listnormal color244 color230
color listnormal_unread color244 color230 bold
color listfocus  color166 color230
color info       color136 color230
color background color244 color230
color article    color244 color230

macro i set browser /usr/bin/feh
macro r set browser /usr/bin/google-chrome-stable
